spec_data.Name: python-unicodecsv
spec_data.Description:
The unicodecsv is a drop-in replacement for Python 2.7's
csv module which supports unicode strings without a hassle.
It is NOT a drop-in replacement for Python 3's csv module,
see https://github.com/jdunck/python-unicodecsv/issues/65
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 04:47:38 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Drop-in replacement for Python 2.7's csv module which supports unicode strings
